## How it works

## Terms at a glance

- **Commission** applies to **all revenue** from your referred client —
  retainers, projects, and any upsells
- **Lifetime means lifetime** — commissions continue for the full duration of
  the client relationship, no cap
- **Referral is tracked** from first introduction — documented in writing so
  there's never ambiguity
- **Payouts** are processed within 7 days of receiving the client's payment
- **No minimum referrals** required — one introduction is enough to be in the
  program
- **You can refer multiple clients** — commissions stack independently per
  client. If you refer 3 clients on retainers, you're earning **$1,500/month**
  passively.

